---

<PageLayout
  title="/uses: Simon's list of things"
  description="An evolving list of things I use and enjoy. Lights, microphones, camera, software and all!"
  gradientStart="from-cyan-400"
  gradientEnd="to-sky-500"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl pt-10">
    <IntroText
      >Almost every day, I get asked about my vscode color theme and font, what microphone I use,
      what camera lens I recommend. Here's a non-exhaustive and evolving list of the things I own
      and recommend :)
    </IntroText>

