            <hr />
            <h2>Code editor</h2>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Code editor</strong>: <a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/">VS Code</a> as my code editor.</li>
              <li><strong>Color theme</strong>: <a
                  href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=sdras.night-owl"
                  >Night Owl</a
                > by Sarah Drasner.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Font</strong>: <a
                  href="https://philpl.gumroad.com/l/dank-mono?a=810537075">Dank Mono</a
                > by Phil Pluckthun.
              </li>
            </ul>
            <h2>Video stuff</h2>
            <ul>
              <li>
                <strong>Camera</strong>: <a href="https://amzn.to/423jjgO">Sony alpha 6100</a>. It has great
                colors and amazing autofocus.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Lens</strong>: <a href="https://amzn.to/41G4yR6">Sigma 16mm F/1.4</a>. Blurry background and cinematic look. This might be my favourite piece of equipment â€”Â I LOVE it.
              </li>
